posts.post_content:
I have a complete PSA graded T201 set that I am looking to sell. All cards are PSA graded and range from 1 - 4.5. I am in the process of scanning the front and back of each card. Let me know if you are interested and I will get you scans.

Looking for $2,000.00 obo/dlvd via money order or Paypal gift.

Matt

I have scanned in all cards. The Lobert/Moore card was once owned by Jeff Burdick so I will find a replacement card for this slot if you are interested.

Matt
